Package: surveyMeta
Title: Extract Structured Metadata from Social Survey Documents Using LLM APIs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sho Fujihara [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7007-1934>)
Maintainer: Sho Fujihara <fujihara@iss.u-tokyo.ac.jp>
Authors@R: person("Sho", "Fujihara", email = "fujihara@iss.u-tokyo.ac.jp",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7007-1934"))
Description: Extracts structured metadata from social survey documents (questionnaires,
    reports) using LLM APIs (Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini). Outputs metadata conforming
    to the JDCat/DDI schema with controlled vocabulary mapping for CESSDA topics, DDI
    sampling procedures, and DDI modes of collection. Supports text extraction, PDF vision,
    and hybrid modes for optimal handling of diverse document quality.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
